rows.label: qst200221_msg0001
rows.name:
Finally found you.
You are Harghal, right?!

rows.label: qst200221_msg0002
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Who are you?
New people from the supplier?

rows.label: qst200221_msg0003
rows.name:
No, wrong!
I am an ally of justice
who has come to save you!

rows.label: qst200221_msg0005
rows.name:
I know everything about you!
Why did you dye your hands
in smuggling Pollen Orbs!

rows.label: qst200221_msg0007
rows.name:
What's wrong?
Why are you silent?

rows.label: qst200221_msg0009
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Why do you look away?
Are you still hiding something?

rows.label: qst200221_msg0012
rows.name:
Hmm[ML:Dash ]
It appears she is making something
using Pollen Orbs as ingredients, no?

rows.label: qst200221_msg0013
rows.name:
What does this mean, Harghal?
Are you not smuggling Pollen Orbs!?

rows.label: qst200221_msg0014
rows.name: What on earth are you hiding!?

rows.label: qst200221_msg0017
rows.name: In that case, I'll get serious too!!
